{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-02",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_02_hammett_128kb.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Death in the Fog",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 6,
  "page_total": 6,
  "page_start_sec": 1217.24,
  "page_end_sec": 1451.06,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.738,
  "corrected": "claude",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 1217.24,
      "end": 1218.14,
      "text": "\"Did you see anybody that—",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1218.26,
      "end": 1218.5,
      "text": "?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1219.22,
      "end": 1219.8,
      "text": "\"No,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1219.84,
      "end": 1220.62,
      "text": "no witnesses,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1221.06,
      "end": 1222.66,
      "text": "Spade said and laughed pleasantly."
    },
    {
      "start": 1223.54,
      "end": 1223.92,
      "text": "\"Sit down,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1224.0,
      "end": 1224.4,
      "text": "Dundy."
    },
    {
      "start": 1224.5,
      "end": 1225.94,
      "text": "You haven't finished your drink."
    },
    {
      "start": 1226.52,
      "end": 1227.14,
      "text": "Get your glass,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1227.26,
      "end": 1227.46,
      "text": "Tom.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1228.704,
      "end": 1229.14,
      "text": "Tom said:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1229.34,
      "end": 1230.02,
      "text": "\"No, thanks,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1230.24,
      "end": 1230.42,
      "text": "Sam.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1231.712,
      "end": 1232.54,
      "text": "Dundy sat down,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1232.62,
      "end": 1234.62,
      "text": "but paid no attention to his glass of rum."
    },
    {
      "start": 1235.84,
      "end": 1236.98,
      "text": "Spade filled his own glass,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1237.18,
      "end": 1237.58,
      "text": "drank,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1237.98,
      "end": 1239.66,
      "text": "set the empty glass on the table,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1239.68,
      "end": 1241.18,
      "text": "and returned to his bedside-seat."
    },
    {
      "start": 1242.28,
      "end": 1243.38,
      "text": "\"I know where I stand now,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1243.54,
      "end": 1243.94,
      "text": "he said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1244.04,
      "end": 1245.72,
      "text": "looking with friendly eyes from one"
    },
    {
      "start": 1245.72,
      "end": 1247.22,
      "text": "of the police-detectives to the other."
    },
    {
      "start": 1248.12,
      "end": 1249.78,
      "text": "\"I'm sorry I got up on my hind legs,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1250.3,
      "end": 1252.94,
      "text": "but you birds coming in and trying to put the work on me"
    },
    {
      "start": 1253.28,
      "end": 1253.96,
      "text": "made me nervous."
    },
    {
      "start": 1255.04,
      "end": 1256.6,
      "text": "Having Miles knocked off bothered me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1256.68,
      "end": 1258.72,
      "text": "and then you birds cracking foxy."
    },
    {
      "start": 1259.48,
      "end": 1260.16,
      "text": "That's all right now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1260.28,
      "end": 1260.52,
      "text": "though,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1260.58,
      "end": 1262.42,
      "text": "now that I know what you're up to.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1262.64,
      "end": 1263.78,
      "text": "Tom said:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1264.0,
      "end": 1264.86,
      "text": "\"Forget it.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1265.72,
      "end": 1266.06,
      "text": "The Lieutenant",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1266.32,
      "end": 1266.78,
      "text": "said nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 1267.936,
      "end": 1268.5,
      "text": "Spade asked:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1269.184,
      "end": 1269.7,
      "text": "\"Thursby die?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1270.82,
      "end": 1271.92,
      "text": "While the Lieutenant hesitated,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1272.08,
      "end": 1272.6,
      "text": "Tom said:"
    },
    {
      "start": 1272.8,
      "end": 1273.38,
      "text": "\"Yes.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1274.68,
      "end": 1274.88,
      "text": "Then the",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1275.0,
      "end": 1276.09,
      "text": "Lieutenant said angrily:"
    },
    {
      "start": 1276.12,
      "end": 1278.4,
      "text": "\"And you might just as well know it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1278.44,
      "end": 1279.48,
      "text": "if you don't,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1279.78,
      "end": 1280.54,
      "text": "that he died before"
    },
    {
      "start": 1280.54,
      "end": 1281.76,
      "text": "he could tell anybody anything.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1283.04,
      "end": 1284.24,
      "text": "Spade was rolling a cigarette.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1284.46,
      "end": 1285.22,
      "text": "He asked,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1285.28,
      "end": 1285.96,
      "text": "not looking up:"
    },
    {
      "start": 1286.66,
      "end": 1287.59,
      "text": "\"What do you mean by that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1287.9,
      "end": 1289.6,
      "text": "You think I did know it?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1290.72,
      "end": 1291.6,
      "text": "\"I meant what I said,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1291.76,
      "end": 1293.02,
      "text": "Dundy replied bluntly."
    },
    {
      "start": 1294.208,
      "end": 1295.44,
      "text": "Spade looked up at him and smiled,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1295.66,
      "end": 1297.46,
      "text": "holding the finished cigarette in one hand,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1297.9,
      "end": 1298.84,
      "text": "his lighter in the other."
    },
    {
      "start": 1299.86,
      "end": 1301.18,
      "text": "\"You're not ready to pinch me yet,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1301.3,
      "end": 1301.68,
      "text": "are you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1301.7,
      "end": 1302.1,
      "text": "Dundy?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1302.4,
      "end": 1302.82,
      "text": "he asked."
    },
    {
      "start": 1303.968,
      "end": 1307.22,
      "text": "Dundy looked with hard green eyes at Spade and did not answer him.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1308.18,
      "end": 1308.4,
      "text": "\"Then,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1308.6,
      "end": 1309.46,
      "text": "said Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1309.7,
      "end": 1313.72,
      "text": "\"there's no particular reason why I should give a damn what you think,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1313.8,
      "end": 1314.34,
      "text": "is there,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1314.38,
      "end": 1314.78,
      "text": "Dundy?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1315.84,
      "end": 1316.3,
      "text": "Tom said:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1316.6,
      "end": 1317.14,
      "text": "\"Aw,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1317.38,
      "end": 1318.28,
      "text": "be reasonable,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1318.44,
      "end": 1318.66,
      "text": "Sam.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1319.08,
      "end": 1321.62,
      "text": "Spade put the cigarette in his mouth,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1322.06,
      "end": 1322.98,
      "text": "set fire to it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1322.98,
      "end": 1324.1,
      "text": "and laughed smoke out."
    },
    {
      "start": 1325.0,
      "end": 1325.6,
      "text": "\"I'll be reasonable,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1325.74,
      "end": 1326.0,
      "text": "Tom,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1326.14,
      "end": 1326.6,
      "text": "he promised."
    },
    {
      "start": 1326.84,
      "end": 1328.04,
      "text": "\"How did I kill this"
    },
    {
      "start": 1328.28,
      "end": 1328.56,
      "text": "Thursby?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1328.66,
      "end": 1329.26,
      "text": "I've forgotten.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1330.624,
      "end": 1331.84,
      "text": "Tom grunted disgust.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1332.608,
      "end": 1335.44,
      "text": "Lieutenant Dundy said: \"He was shot four times"
    },
    {
      "start": 1335.58,
      "end": 1338.76,
      "text": "in the back, with a forty-four or forty-five, from across the street"
    },
    {
      "start": 1339.28,
      "end": 1341.08,
      "text": "when he started to go in the hotel."
    },
    {
      "start": 1342.176,
      "end": 1342.86,
      "text": "Nobody saw it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1342.88,
      "end": 1344.18,
      "text": "but that's the way it figures.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1344.6,
      "end": 1347.44,
      "text": "\"And he was wearing a Luger in a shoulder-holster,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1347.72,
      "end": 1348.2,
      "text": "Tom added."
    },
    {
      "start": 1348.36,
      "end": 1349.6,
      "text": "\"It hadn't been fired.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1350.2,
      "end": 1352.56,
      "text": "\"What do the hotel-people know about him?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1352.68,
      "end": 1353.38,
      "text": "Spade asked."
    },
    {
      "start": 1354.6,
      "end": 1356.44,
      "text": "\"Nothing except that he'd been there a week.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1357.26,
      "end": 1357.56,
      "text": "\"Alone?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1358.34,
      "end": 1359.22,
      "text": "\"Alone.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1360.15,
      "end": 1362.64,
      "text": "\"What did you find on him? or in his room?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1363.84,
      "end": 1365.38,
      "text": "Dundy drew his lips in and asked:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1365.74,
      "end": 1367.24,
      "text": "\"What'd you think we'd find?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1368.48,
      "end": 1370.82,
      "text": "Spade made a careless circle with his limp cigarette.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1371.552,
      "end": 1373.12,
      "text": "\"Something to tell you who he was,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1373.54,
      "end": 1374.42,
      "text": "what his story was."
    },
    {
      "start": 1375.26,
      "end": 1375.58,
      "text": "Did you?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1376.84,
      "end": 1378.14,
      "text": "\"We thought you could tell us that.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1379.264,
      "end": 1381.76,
      "text": "Spade looked at the Lieutenant with yellow-grey eyes",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1382.02,
      "end": 1384.7,
      "text": "that held an almost exaggerated amount of candor."
    },
    {
      "start": 1385.6,
      "end": 1387.84,
      "text": "\"I've never seen Thursby, dead or alive.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1389.12,
      "end": 1391.1,
      "text": "Lieutenant Dundy stood up looking dissatisfied.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1391.904,
      "end": 1393.32,
      "text": "Tom rose yawning and stretching."
    },
    {
      "start": 1394.74,
      "end": 1396.12,
      "text": "\"We've asked what we came to ask,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1396.28,
      "end": 1397.0,
      "text": "Dundy said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1397.664,
      "end": 1399.5,
      "text": "frowning over eyes hard as green pebbles."
    },
    {
      "start": 1400.22,
      "end": 1401.98,
      "text": "He held his mustached upper lip"
    },
    {
      "start": 1402.5,
      "end": 1403.22,
      "text": "tight to his teeth,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1404.064,
      "end": 1405.8,
      "text": "letting his lower lip push the words out."
    },
    {
      "start": 1406.84,
      "end": 1408.54,
      "text": "\"We've told you more than you've told us."
    },
    {
      "start": 1409.44,
      "end": 1410.08,
      "text": "That's fair enough."
    },
    {
      "start": 1410.9,
      "end": 1411.36,
      "text": "You know me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1411.44,
      "end": 1411.8,
      "text": "Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 1412.09,
      "end": 1413.68,
      "text": "If you did or you didn't,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1413.68,
      "end": 1415.38,
      "text": "you'll get a square deal out of me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1415.98,
      "end": 1416.82,
      "text": "and most of the breaks."
    },
    {
      "start": 1417.62,
      "end": 1420.3,
      "text": "I don't know that I'd blame you a hell of a lot,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1420.48,
      "end": 1422.58,
      "text": "but that wouldn't keep me from nailing you.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1423.72,
      "end": 1424.08,
      "text": "\"Fair enough,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1424.36,
      "end": 1425.62,
      "text": "Spade replied evenly."
    },
    {
      "start": 1426.48,
      "end": 1428.88,
      "text": "\"But I'd feel better about it if you'd drink your drink.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1430.4,
      "end": 1431.92,
      "text": "Lieutenant Dundy turned to the table,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1432.04,
      "end": 1432.94,
      "text": "picked up his glass,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1432.98,
      "end": 1433.98,
      "text": "and slowly emptied it."
    },
    {
      "start": 1434.64,
      "end": 1435.14,
      "text": "Then he said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1435.58,
      "end": 1435.94,
      "text": "\"Good night,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1436.5,
      "end": 1437.36,
      "text": "and held out his hand."
    },
    {
      "start": 1437.78,
      "end": 1440.0,
      "text": "They shook hands ceremoniously."
    },
    {
      "start": 1440.18,
      "end": 1442.54,
      "text": "Tom and Spade shook hands ceremoniously."
    },
    {
      "start": 1442.92,
      "end": 1444.3,
      "text": "Spade let them out."
    },
    {
      "start": 1445.72,
      "end": 1446.24,
      "text": "Then he undressed,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1446.88,
      "end": 1447.68,
      "text": "turned off the lights,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1447.76,
      "end": 1448.68,
      "text": "and went to bed."
    },
    {
      "start": 1450.016,
      "end": 1451.06,
      "text": "End of chapter two."
    }
  ]
}